<li id="cite_note-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Slattery, Martin (2003). <i>Key Ideas In Sociology</i>. Nelson Thornes. pp.&#160;154+.</span></span></li>
